{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"fb6b39f9-1c85-43ef-9b17-3be15f9ffb5d","content":"In your `App.xaml.cs`, override `CreateWindow` and subscribe to the lifecycle events:\n\n```csharp\nprotected override Window CreateWindow(IActivationState? activationState)\n{\n    var window = base.CreateWindow(activationState);\n\n    window.Created += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Created\");\n    window.Activated += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Activated\");\n    window.Deactivated += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Deactivated\");\n    window.Stopped += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Stopped\");\n    window.Resumed += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Resumed\");\n    window.Destroying += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Destroying\");\n    window.Backgrounding += (s, e) => Debug.WriteLine(\"Window Backgrounding\");\n\n    return window;\n}\n```\n\n**Event flow:**\n\n| Transition | Events fired |\n|---|---|\n| App launch | Created → Activated |\n| App goes to background | Deactivated → Stopped (→ Backgrounding on iOS/Mac) |\n| App returns to foreground | Resumed → Activated |\n| App closed | Destroying |\n\n> `Backgrounding` only fires on iOS/Mac Catalyst and provides a `BackgroundingEventArgs` with a `State` dictionary you can use to persist data.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c775b81b-635e-4493-b5bd-8a077a5fab5c","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about subscribing to Window lifecycle events in a .NET MAUI app for debugging/logging purposes. This is a general knowledge question about .NET MAUI that I can answer directly without needing to search the codebase.\n\nIn .NET MAUI, the `Window` class exposes several lifecycle events that correspond to platform-specific states. Let me provide a concise, helpful answer.\n\nThe Window lifecycle events in .NET MAUI are:\n- Created\n- Activated\n- Deactivated\n- Stopped\n- Resumed\n- Destroying\n- Backgrounding (iOS/Mac Catalyst)\n\n\nNow I'll show how to subscribe to these events with a practical example.","outputTokens":504,"requestId":"A42D:3B9434:5DEA90A:6665A35:69F0050A"},"id":"001b5361-c3f0-4d22-b62f-38de68f3a438","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:53:39.753Z","parentId":"47415b53-0a46-467a-8b4d-61f5a9fd1959"}
